<p>63 mins: Off the line!</p>

<p>United break in numbers and Ighalo chooses to go alone, his shot blocked by a defender.</p>

<p>Mata retrieves it on the right and finds Lingard at the back post, who sees his volley blocked byÂ Ryan Tunnicliffe with the keeper beaten.</p>

<p>57 mins: Still a tight gameÂ  here. United moving the ball a little better since the break.</p>

